Package org.vostok.lang.classes.bytecode

This package provides classes for direct action on byte code.

          Description

Class Summary
RawClassDecoding this class is primary intended to look for basic informationson a class (such as class name, interfaces, runtime annotations...), from a binary stream, a file or an url without the need of loading the class.
 

Package org.vostok.lang.classes.bytecode Description

This package provides classes for direct action on byte code.
Adds 1 new classe :

  • RawClassDecoding : a simple - and fast - byte code decoding, intended to collect basic informations such as class name, interfaces, runtime annotations, on a class directly from byte data (inputStream, File, url...)
